  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "summary",
      "abstract": "Commencing January 1, 2027, mandates insurers provide health insurance coverage without cost-share requirements for vaccinations recommended by the DOH and mandates the coverage for the medical assistance program and managed care organizations."
